  "title": "Marketing and Sales Manager (Precious Metals)",
  "description": "<p>You will drive our market growth by aligning high-impact brand strategies with direct sales efforts to acquire and maintain institutional and individual private bullion investors. This role requires both commercial market acumen and product/services domain knowledge to structure physical precious metals and hedging transactions.</p><p>Core Requirements</p><p>• Sales Pipeline Architecture: Proven ability to build and manage a lead-to-close pipeline specifically tailored for high-net-worth (HNW) and institutional precious metals investors.</p><p>• Strategic Market Positioning: Expertise in developing marketing campaigns that communicate trust, security, and value in the volatile Gold, Silver, and PGM markets.</p><p>• Commercial Closing: Skilled at navigating the full sales cycle, from presenting market insights and hedging strategies to finalizing high-value bullion contracts.</p><p>• Campaign & Content Oversight: Ability to produce authoritative market commentary and educational content that establishes the firm as a thought leader in the precious metals space.</p><p>•  Regulatory & Risk Literacy: A strong understanding of the compliance requirements (AML/KYC) and market mechanics unique to the trading of physical commodities.</p>",
