    "description": "<p>As Singapore's homegrown and leading Precious Metals dealer, GoldSilver Central is proud to offer the most market competitive, real-time pricing over a wide range of products and services on three distinctive groups of Precious Metals, Gold, Silver and Platinum. Backed by a knowledgeable team of financial market professionals with strong financial expertise and experience in Precious Metals, we partner investors who are keen to diversify their financial portfolio.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Having amassed a decade of proven track record and industry recognition, we now seek driven and passionate individuals who are keen to make things happen, identify and leverage on new business opportunities. With many new exciting plans on the near horizon, we invite you to embark on a successful and rewarding career in an interdependent team with a strong camaraderie.</p>",
